{"tid":2327712,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蔡英文總統：基於對民主自由價值的堅持，我要公開聲援黎智英先生。","createTime":"2020-12-16T09:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T13:06:33.000Z","uid":310867,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9947df3dfcd563d16c01e8ecdf41514772aad2","tid":2327712,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"幾天前，壹傳媒的創辦人黎智英先生，被控涉嫌違反「港版國安法」。這幾天在社群媒體上，不斷出現他被押往香港法院時，雙手上銬、腰部被鐵鍊纏繞的照片，這個畫面令人憤怒，也不忍。<br />\n<br />\n我認識黎先生多年，他的政治理念跟我不盡相同，但我很佩服他經營企業的膽識，以及對香港的由衷熱愛。這次黎先生的遭遇，讓人感嘆香港人民感到驕傲的自由和法治精神，已經成了昨日黃花。<br />\n<br />\n這個幾近羞辱的畫面，正在造成寒蟬效應。北京和香港當局對民主自由的戕害，令人想起台灣在威權統治的年代，雷震先生因為「自由中國」的言論遭到關押時，胡適先生曾經餽贈抒懷的詩句「萬山不許一溪奔」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">世界人權日才剛過，香港自由人權的寒冬卻正凜冽。基於對民主自由價值的堅持，我要公開聲援黎智英先生。我希望讓他知道，全台灣、全世界都在看著這一幕。被羞辱的不是黎先生，而是香港的自由和法治。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201216/L6WQWCQLVFARXEHZRBJPRI232Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201216%2FL6WQWCQLVFARXEHZRBJPRI232Y%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMUy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=52409e5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201216%2FL6WQWCQLVFARXEHZRBJPRI232Y%2F&h=9a88b604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201216/L6WQWCQLVFARXEHZRBJPRI232Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d42873bbcd446090ca464d0df044263dcabef6","tid":2327712,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6f6a7a52508ccc8897242fd2566a872bf04a48","tid":2327712,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2298d269085ddff05cdb7a8c15e6549b95860d6d","tid":2327712,"uid":76609,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:22:24.000Z","msg":"連登仔：蔡英文唔識政治"},{"pid":"eb93fffc8be28fde745a66908ef07995b0ec772a","tid":2327712,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2298d269085ddff05cdb7a8c15e6549b95860d6d","tid":2327712,"uid":76609,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:22:24.000Z","msg":"連登仔：蔡英文唔識政治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"要搏口交部回應同時見下媒體好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa283d3b93acda5cbf44c8c08cb7582d0d23820","tid":2327712,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"c45265de6faec615bf58e31a2d1ce455063853b0","tid":2327712,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:33:06.000Z","msg":"公開聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf6208315abcfdafda4f52cb18cf27c6ca70d76","tid":2327712,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"呀祖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1f459a20349bd0922c6075c527a0778cb8c6e6","tid":2327712,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bf6208315abcfdafda4f52cb18cf27c6ca70d76","tid":2327712,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"呀祖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"呀祖諗緊點樣取消所有香港法案"},{"pid":"0eacb1939053c354ad3957121c4484bfca5d2ffb","tid":2327712,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img sr